ğŸš€ MERN Chat AI Developer

MERN Chat AI Developer is a cutting-edge AI-powered chat application built with the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express, React, Node.js). It assists developers with smart code suggestions, in-app code execution, and seamless integration with GitHub and LinkedIn for effortless sharing and networking.

ğŸ“ Key Features
ğŸ’¡ AI-Powered Code Assistance
Real-Time Suggestions: Context-aware code suggestions as you type.

Smart Autocomplete: Complete functions and blocks with AI-driven predictions.

Instant Debugging: Detects errors and proposes quick fixes.

ğŸ’» Code Execution & Snippet Management
In-App Execution: Run your code instantly without external tools.

Multi-Language Support: Supports JavaScript, Python, Java, C++, and more.

Personal Snippet Library: Save, organize, and reuse your code snippets anytime.

ğŸ“Š Personal Dashboard
Customized Dashboard: View and manage all your projects, snippets, and AI suggestions in one place.

Project Analytics: Get insights into execution history and AI usage.

ğŸ”— Seamless Integrations
Download Code: Export your snippets and projects directly to your local machine.

GitHub Upload: Push your code to GitHub repositories with a single click.

LinkedIn Sharing: Post your coding milestones and updates on LinkedIn to showcase your work.

ğŸ¨ Customizable UI
Dark & Light Modes: Switch themes as per your preference.

Fully Responsive: Smooth experience across desktops, tablets, and mobile devices.

