ğŸ“¦ Installation
bash
Copy
Edit
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/mern-chat-ai-developer.git
cd mern-chat-ai-developer

# Install backend dependencies
npm install

# Install frontend dependencies
cd client
npm install

# Run the application
cd ..
npm run dev
By default, the app runs on http://localhost:3000.

